"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president gave a long speech where he spoke to his supporters and challenged his opponents. This was reported by the BBC's Anthony Zurcher.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President's Speech\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos dio un discurso largo donde habl\u00f3 a sus seguidores y desafi\u00f3 a sus oponentes. Esto fue reportado por Anthony Zurcher de la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Discurso del Presidente de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Events took place all over Ukraine to remember four years since Russia started its large-scale invasion.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Remembers Invasion\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hubo eventos en toda Ucrania para recordar cuatro a\u00f1os desde que Rusia comenz\u00f3 su gran invasi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Recuerda Invasi\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Friedrich Merz said it would be wrong for Germany to separate from China. He said this just before flying to Beijing.\",            \"english_title\": \"Germany and China Relations\",            \"translated_version\": \"Friedrich Merz dijo que ser\u00eda malo para Alemania separarse de China. Dijo esto justo antes de volar a Beijing.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Relaciones Alemania y China\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The remote Yonaguni island is important because it is near Taiwan, which is having more problems with China.\",            \"english_title\": \"Yonaguni Island's Importance\",            \"translated_version\": \"La isla remota Yonaguni es importante porque est\u00e1 cerca de Taiw\u00e1n, que tiene m\u00e1s problemas con China.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Importancia de la Isla Yonaguni\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"There have been more attacks in the Kordofan region, causing many deaths, and peace is still hard to achieve.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kordofan Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ha habido m\u00e1s ataques en la regi\u00f3n de Kordof\u00e1n, causando muchas muertes, y la paz sigue siendo dif\u00edcil de lograr.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques en Kordof\u00e1n\"        }    ]}"